\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add spinach and tomatoes, stir with spatula then leave to rest for 5 minutes. Flake cooked salmon into pieces. Serve immediately with orzo, sprinkled with pepper."}],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","40m","4 portions"]}